{"tid":2429413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（Condom) K11 MUSEA將終止名潮食館租約","createTime":"2021-03-02T09:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T10:41:45.000Z","uid":230530,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b91ec5d43de3daecd29a549d8b4a67540e54984","tid":2429413,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"K11 MUSEA「名潮食館」近日出現超級傳播，政府專家顧問袁國勇指餐廳所釋出的鮮風量只有申請牌照時說明的3分1。K11集團表示，將終止「名潮食館」的租約。<br />\n<br />\nK11集團發言人強調，名潮食館的通風系統屬獨立運作，與其他商戶及食肆並不相連，商場內的通風系統，接近醫院使用的最高級別，在出風前更設有UV消毒，衛生水平高，不受個別租戶自設的通風系統影響。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，集團會繼續在場內進行深層清潔及消毒，為本周六重開作準備，商場亦將於明天為商場員工安排第二次檢測，商場員工須出示陰性檢測證明才可上班。"},{"pid":"65e22f0dc487067c9936e23549641630a3eb941d","tid":2429413,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"名潮邊個老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b539bf759363471c69514fe339f86221dbe4a9df","tid":2429413,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"多謝袁國勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366112161a5e0370e678650069786cca45cbc3e7","tid":2429413,"uid":165200,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"65e22f0dc487067c9936e23549641630a3eb941d","tid":2429413,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"名潮邊個老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"朱元璋（好似係）"},{"pid":"a15968bf96e4684e6abc208d84c403caf38a4f4a","tid":2429413,"uid":79789,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"366112161a5e0370e678650069786cca45cbc3e7","tid":2429413,"uid":165200,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"65e22f0dc487067c9936e23549641630a3eb941d","tid":2429413,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T09:31:49.000Z","msg"